Subject: [PATCH 3/3] feat(setup): voice profile audio preview button
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Each profile SKU card now has a ▶/❚❚ preview button. Plays a 5s
sample of that voice via a shared <audio> ref. Tracks playingSku
state so the icon updates correctly + auto-resets when audio
ends/errors.

Mapping:
  standard    -> meera
  clinic      -> pavithra
  real_estate -> arvind
  premium     -> meera

Sample URLs are derived from NEXT_PUBLIC_VOICE_SAMPLE_BASE_URL env
(e.g. a Supabase Storage public bucket). Button is disabled with a
tooltip if the env isn't set or sample is missing (404).

To enable: upload meera.mp3 / pavithra.mp3 / arvind.mp3 to a public
Supabase Storage bucket and set NEXT_PUBLIC_VOICE_SAMPLE_BASE_URL=
https://YOUR_PROJECT.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/voice-samples
in dashboard/.env.
